  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/88d1d978f776c46b1c531a757d7d015f.poster.avif?t=1757937643\" width=604 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/88d1d978f776c46b1c531a757d7d015f.webm?t=1757937643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/88d1d978f776c46b1c531a757d7d015f.mp4?t=1757937643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/1713370925bbeb076f2eb770046076ae.avif?t=1757937643\" width=604 height=128 /></span><br>The King is tired of being protected so now he is shooting the enemies down! King Bullseye is a shoot-the-target game in which the enemies are chess pieces on the board! Can you think quickly to predict who you need to destroy first?<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/a1d1c5be09766cc4ad1aa193bfcc8480.avif?t=1757937643\" width=604 height=128 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Eliminate the enemies before they reach the King!<br></li><li> Enemies make a move per \"turn\". Harder enemies make two or three steps per \"turn\".<br></li><li> Headshots increase your score multiplier up to 10x!<br></li><li> Miss shots or shots to the body decrease your multiplier!<br></li><li> At the end of each wave you'll receive a bonus score for time and shields remaining.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/2d985b0846e81b7b38facb057aa91785.poster.avif?t=1757937643\" width=604 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/2d985b0846e81b7b38facb057aa91785.webm?t=1757937643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/2d985b0846e81b7b38facb057aa91785.mp4?t=1757937643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/123fb349927b36f2d0e08802b34330de.avif?t=1757937643\" width=604 height=128 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Leaderboard: Fight for the highscore. (Steam Integration)<br></li><li>Achievements: 26 achievements to conquer. (Steam Integration)<br></li><li>Light Gun Support: Light Gun is supported via the absolute mouse coordinates, you'll need to activate it on the pause menu!<br></li><li>Mouse Sensitivity: Configurable via the pause menu<br></li><li>Never Dies Mode: Keep playing even if you lose. Your score will stop increasing but you can keep training!<br></li><li>Waves: 3 waves that mix different enemies with their patterns and difficulty.<br></li><li>Straight to Action: No running around with lots of texts or customizations that take hours. Just enjoy a single-player campaign full of action and challenge!<br></li><li>Play-Only Controller Support: You can use a controller to move the crosshair and shoot, but the pause menu needs a mouse. (It might be too difficult on the controller though)<br></li><li>Steam Cloud Integration</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/1f04936895a25b9d3f135723ea89e93c.poster.avif?t=1757937643\" width=604 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/1f04936895a25b9d3f135723ea89e93c.webm?t=1757937643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600870/extras/1f04936895a25b9d3f135723ea89e93c.mp4?t=1757937643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
